data.description: Welcome home to a serene rural lake community! This charming farmhouse style home offers an abundance of space and potential. Come experience the inviting charm of this gem. The heart of this home is the cozy living area and eat-in kitchen, ideal for gatherings. The spacious master bedroom provides a peaceful sanctuary after a long day. The new bathroom insert (in box) conveys and awaits installation. The included washer, dryer, and refrigerator eliminate the stress of purchasing new appliances. For those seeking a little extra room to roam, THIS PROPERTY COMES WITH AN EXTRA LOT. Selling AS-IS, this home provides a canvas for those with a vision to put their personal touch on every detail. Embrace the freedom to customize and make it uniquely yours, creating the perfect space for you and your loved ones. Just a few minutes from Cedar Creek Lake, one of the largest lakes in Texas and home to great boating and bass fishing. Your peaceful, rural haven awaits just an hour from Dallas!
